{"version":2,"title":"Jordan, Robert - The Wheel of Time Omnibus [Complete Series In 1 Book]","author":"Jordan, Robert","state":{"lastAnalyzedIndex":46,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"Lews Therin Telamon","aliases":["Dragon"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"And it came to pass in those days","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A powerful and proud channeller who led the fight against the Shadow.","relationships":[{"character":"Ilyena Sunhair","relationship":"Wife"},{"character":"The Betrayer","relationship":"Enemy"}],"recentEvents":"Lews Therin faces his guilt over his actions that led to the Breaking of the World, his wife's death, and channels the One Power in a destructive act."},{"name":"The Betrayer","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"And it came to pass in those days","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A powerful channeller who aided the Shadow against Lews Therin.","relationships":[{"character":"Lews Therin Telamon","relationship":"Enemy"}],"recentEvents":"The Betrayer confronts Lews Therin about his past actions and the breaking of the world, and warns him that the conflict between them will continue until the end of time."},{"name":"Rand al'Thor","aliases":["Rand","Dunser"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Shadow in the Inn","currentLocation":"Emond's Field","description":"A young man from Emond's Field who is about to begin a grand adventure.","relationships":[{"character":"Moiraine Damodred","relationship":"Traveled with during perilous adventures"},{"character":"Lan Mandragoran","relationship":"Traveled with during perilous adventures"},{"character":"Mat Cauthon","relationship":"Traveled with during perilous adventures"}],"recentEvents":"Fled from the inn with Moiraine and Lan after her speech about Manetheren's history, followed by Mat"},{"name":"Matrim Cauthon","aliases":["Mat"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: The Peddler","currentLocation":