n and potential fireworks."},{"name":"Cenn Buie","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"A Prophecy Fulfilled","currentLocation":"Emond's Field","description":"A sceptical villager who has little faith in the coming festival activities.","relationships":[{"character":"Bran al'Vere","relationship":"disagrees with the mayor on various issues and feels skeptical"},{"character":"Master al'Vere","relationship":"knows him as a blacksmith"}],"recentEvents":"Expressed skepticism about the arrival of the gleeman and the prospects of fireworks."},{"name":"Egwene al'Vere","aliases":["Egwene"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: The Peddler","currentLocation":"Emond's Field, Two Rivers","description":"Has a gift for prophecy and a special connection to Moiraine.","relationships":[{"character":"Rand al'Thor","relationship":"friend"},{"character":"Matrim Cauthon","relationship":"friend"},{"character":"Perrin Aybara","relationship":"friend"}],"recentEvents":"Not present in this chapter."}],"locations":[{"name":"The Land","description":"A place where the Shadow fell and the world was broken by Lews Therin's destructive act."},{"name":"Island","description":"An island formed by the lava flow from the mountain created by Lews Therin's channeling of the One Power."},{"name":"Emond's Field","description":"A small village in the Two Rivers with a blacksmith and an inn, currently preparing for the Bel Tine festival and discussing the arrival of a gleeman and the possibility of fireworks."}],"summary":"Rand, Mat, and Egwene meet the mysterious Moiraine and her Warder Lan, who gives them silver pennies for potential future tasks. They discuss the significance of their encounter and speculate about Moiraine's purpose in the Two Rivers."}},{"index":40,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"Lews Therin Telamon","aliases":["Dragon"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"And it came to pass in those days","currentLocation":"Unknown","descr