 Two Rivers, characterized by its agricultural lifestyle and tight-knit community."},{"name":"The Village Council","description":"An assembly of respected members within the community who meet to discuss and decide on matters concerning Emond's Field."},{"name":"Forest near Emond's Field","description":"A place where Rand finds himself after fleeing the village that was captured by Trollocs."},{"name":"House of Tam al'Thor","description":"The home where Rand and Tam live, now left in ruins after being attacked by Trollocs."},{"name":"Barn of Tam al'Thor","description":"The barn where Rand seeks supplies but finds it in shambles with animals and carts gone."}],"summary":"Rand struggles to gather supplies while saving his sick father from a lone Trolloc that attacked them in their ruined home. Carrying his father to Emond's Field for medical help, Rand fights against the worsening condition of Tam as he is beset by nightmares and the chaos of war."}},{"index":43,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"Lews Therin Telamon","aliases":["Dragon"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"And it came to pass in those days","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A powerful and proud channeller who led the fight against the Shadow.","relationships":[{"character":"Ilyena Sunhair","relationship":"Wife"},{"character":"The Betrayer","relationship":"Enemy"}],"recentEvents":"Lews Therin faces his guilt over his actions that led to the Breaking of the World, his wife's death, and channels the One Power in a destructive act."},{"name":"The Betrayer","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"And it came to pass in those days","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A powerful channeller who aided the Shadow against Lews Therin.","relationships":[{"character":"Lews Therin Telamon","relationship":"Enemy"}],"recentEvents":"The Betrayer confronts Lews Therin about his past actions and the breaking of the world, and warns him that the conflict between them 