atus":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: The Peddler","currentLocation":"Emond's Field, Two Rivers","description":"Known for his gambling and joking; may possess a mysterious pendant.","relationships":[{"character":"Rand al'Thor","relationship":"friend"},{"character":"Perrin Aybara","relationship":"friend"},{"character":"Egwene al'Vere","relationship":"friend"}],"recentEvents":"Meets Moiraine and her Warder Lan, receives a silver penny from Moiraine."},{"name":"Bran al'Vere","aliases":["Mayors of Emond's Field","Bran"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"A Prophecy Fulfilled","currentLocation":"Emond's Field","description":"The mayor of Emond's Field who is usually calm and pragmatic.","relationships":[{"character":"Rand al'Thor","relationship":"knows Rand and his father Tam"},{"character":"Master al'Vere","relationship":"respects Master al'Vere as a skilled blacksmith"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed the upcoming Festival and the arrival of a gleeman and potential fireworks."},{"name":"Cenn Buie","aliases":["Cenn"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Village Takes a Council","currentLocation":"Emond's Field","description":"A skeptical and sometimes contentious member of the Village Council.","relationships":[{"character":"Bran al'Thor","relationship":"Council member and occasional antagonist"},{"character":"Tam al'Thor","relationship":"Council colleague, somewhat suspicious of Tam"}],"recentEvents":"Cenn’s skepticism contrasts with the rest of the Council’s decision-making process, highlighting the division in the community over the threat of outsiders and the war."},{"name":"Egwene al'Vere","aliases":["Egwene"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"A Village in the Two Rivers","currentLocation":"Emond's Field","description":"A young woman of the Two Rivers, intelligent and curious, considering becoming a Wisdom.","relationships":[{"character":"Rand al'Thor","relationship":"friend and romantic interest"},{"character":