sed their dislike by leaving the inn when Moiraine's story ended."}],"locations":[{"name":"The Land","description":"A place where the Shadow fell and the world was broken by Lews Therin's destructive act."},{"name":"Island","description":"An island formed by the lava flow from the mountain created by Lews Therin's channeling of the One Power."},{"name":"Emond's Field","description":"A small village with a bustling inn and a long history tied to the fall of Manetheren."},{"name":"The Village Council","description":"An assembly of respected members within the community who meet to discuss and decide on matters concerning Emond's Field."},{"name":"Forest near Emond's Field","description":"A place where Rand finds himself after fleeing the village that was captured by Trollocs."},{"name":"House of Tam al'Thor","description":"The home where Rand and Tam live, now left in ruins after being attacked by Trollocs."},{"name":"Barn of Tam al'Thor","description":"The barn where Rand seeks supplies but finds it in shambles with animals and carts gone."},{"name":"Near Emond's Field forest","description":"A forested area outside of Emond's Field where Rand and Tam are traveling through heavily laden with fear and fatigue."},{"name":"Westwood","description":"A part of Emond's Field where the fires from the Bel Tine festival were burned, causing a stench due to the destruction and presence of dead Trollocs."},{"name":"Home of Mistress al'Vere","description":"A place in Emond's Field where Rand and his unconscious father, Tam, are cared for."}],"summary":"Moiraine tells the history of Manetheren, moving the villagers with her speech and securing her and Lan's place in Emond's Field. After her moving tale, Moiraine, Rand, Mat, and Lan leave the inn secretly, heading out into the night."}}]},"mapState":null}